<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٧٩٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1647">حُمَيْدٍ الطَّوِيلِ: </a>سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسَ بْنَ مَالِكٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَتِ الْأَنْصَارُ يَوْمَ الْخَنْدَقِ تَقُولُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>نَحْنُ الَّذِينَ بَايَعُوا مُحَمَّدَا … عَلَى الْجِهَادِ مَا حَيِينَا أَبَدَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">فَأَجَابَهُمُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>اللَّهُمَّ لَا عَيْشَ إِلَّا عَيْشُ الْآخِرَهْ … فَأَكْرِمِ الْأَنْصَارَ وَالْمُهَاجِرَهْ.»<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>